commit.message:
Merge branch 'develop' into feature/fid-pipeline

* develop: (41 commits)
  Updated licenses as per comment from @dzach in https://github.com/openpnp/openpnp/issues/573#issuecomment-311633280
  One minor revert missed.
  Bring back the ReferenceLoosePartFeeder stuff since the changes are now in Advanced*
  Move new loose feeder stuff into AdvancedLoosePartFeeder
  Renamed several stages to be more descriptive. Minor text updates.
  Revert "Fixes DrawTemplateMatches stage drawing at corner rather than centered."
  Moved default pipelines into the right place. Updated feeder and wizard code to handle the training pipeline.
  Basic code cleanup and reformatting. Moved the thrice duplicated matMaxima into OpenCvUtils and updated references to it.
  Added default path for reading in templates and logging option to ReadTemplateImage.
  Added default path for templates to WriteTemplateImage
  Added ability to create a template for rect parts from package body
  WriteTemplateImage: Added the ability to use package ID for automatic name creation for a template
  Added the ability to use package ID for automatic name creation for a template
  Added orientation line to DrawRotatedRects
  Fixed error in logic, returning the originally detected model instead of null. That lead to false part orientation.
  TemplateFile path was overwritten by file name in WriteTemplateImage
  Fixed caused by reusing object
  Added logging capability to `MatchPartTemplate`
  Improved LoosePartFeederPipeline.xml with drawing of delivered model
  Fixed bug with `templateFile` and `extension` parameters getting overwritten by working values
  ...
